## üîå Story 5: TMF-Compliance (Seamless Integration)
**NOC Context:** "We play nice with your existing stack. Pedkai exposes standard TMF642 Alarms so your legacy OSS can still read our decisions."

### Step 1: Poll Alarms (TMF642)
1.  Find **TMF642 Alarm Management** -> `GET /tmf-api/alarmManagement/v4/alarm`.
2.  Click **Try it out** and **Execute**.
